title: Sophia Bush / Heart Disease in Women
description: Sean asks Priyanka about how she de-stresses as Sean heads into an intense tech week for his new play in Chicago. Sophia Bush sows the seeds of success with her One Tree Hill rewatch podcast and new show Good Sam. Sophia passionately brings awareness to the need for more research into heart disease in women.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
